translate chinese jamiep3_a4b86b2a:

    # gnd "It's hard to make friends as an adult - especially when you spend most of your time at home, like I do."
    gnd "成年人交朋友很难——尤其是像我这样大部分时间都待在家里的人。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep3.rpy:18
translate chinese jamiep3_6a377a93:

    # gnd "That's why I go to Java Lava to have my coffee every morning."
    gnd "这就是为什么我每天早上都要去Java Lava喝咖啡。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep3.rpy:19
translate chinese jamiep3_b4b2cc87:

    # gnd "I get lonely."
    gnd "我会感到孤独。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamiep3.rpy:23
translate chinese jamiep3_ab221d8d:

    # gnd "I know. That's what my dad says too."
